exports[`renderComparisonReport > matches the golden standard-detail snapshot 1`] = `
"---
title: Fundamental LLM model comparison
description: A reproducible, cited comparison of 1 large language models across 1 providers over 2 model×effort configurations — sustained throughput and latency measured separately, empirically tested JSON-schema complexity, length-instruction accuracy, and a per-configuration LLM-judge developer review, each over 3 trials.
